Seongdong-gu, 78-year-old man confirmed pneumonia in Wuhan. Overseas Travel/Confirmers Don't Have Contact

Confirmation of Wuhan Pneumonia (Corona 19) occurred in Seongdong-gu, Seoul. A 78-year-old man who has never traveled abroad and has not had contact with others who have traveled abroad or have been confirmed with SAR-CoV-2 infection.

Seongdong-gu Commissioner Jang Ji-oh said on Monday [17 Feb 2020] that he had a [COVID-19] confirmed person in Seongdong-gu.

[Byline: Park Jin-woo]

